504
00:43:34,729 --> 00:43:37,199
Telepon kita berdering terus karena Joo Hyun.

505
00:43:47,750 --> 00:43:49,520
- Apa petunjukmu?
- Baiklah.

506
00:43:49,520 --> 00:43:51,550
- Kita periksa dahulu.
- Apa alamatnya?

507
00:43:51,550 --> 00:43:52,849
Baiklah, akan kulaporkan ke bosku.

508
00:43:52,849 --> 00:43:54,649
Mungkinkah itu orang lain?

509
00:43:55,089 --> 00:43:56,119
Hei.

510
00:44:01,359 --> 00:44:02,530
Hei, lihat.

511
00:44:12,339 --> 00:44:13,470
Apa?

512
00:44:14,970 --> 00:44:17,240
- Tidak...
- Kamu mau mati?

513
00:44:18,440 --> 00:44:19,980
Tidak...

514
00:44:24,919 --> 00:44:26,250
Dasar...

515
00:44:32,520 --> 00:44:33,559
Selamat berolahraga.

516
00:44:41,369 --> 00:44:42,569
Enam.

517
00:44:43,240 --> 00:44:45,500
Tujuh, delapan...

518
00:44:45,669 --> 00:44:47,339
Baru-baru ini, sebuah agensi berita

519
00:44:47,339 --> 00:44:50,680
