00:48:07,839 --> 00:48:09,909
- Astaga.
- Dia nyaris sampai.

578
00:48:12,309 --> 00:48:14,849
Pak, apakah ada perang?

579
00:48:14,849 --> 00:48:17,119
Ini hanya olahraga.

580
00:48:19,520 --> 00:48:22,649
Ya? Ya. Tolong tunggu sebentar.

581
00:48:22,889 --> 00:48:24,819
Pak, ini untukmu.

582
00:48:25,619 --> 00:48:27,030
- Aku?
- Ya.

583
00:48:31,359 --> 00:48:32,599
- Ya?
- Maafkan aku,

584
00:48:32,599 --> 00:48:34,770
